SUMMARY:高菁晗 (Eileen) · SA Meeting
DESCRIPTION:SA meeting #1\n作业: Hi Eileen\,\n\nOnce again\, great work on th
 e mindmap\, a lot of thoughtful ideas.\n\nI have made some annotations on 
 your ideas. These are the legends:\n\n✅: Very promising to develop into an
  EPQ project \n⭕: Certain potential in developing into an EPQ project\n❌: 
 Too “simple” or unrealistic with current scope \n(e.g. experiment limitati
 ons)\n\nCould you have a look at the annotated mindmap\, and pick three to
 pics (could be single ones or a combination of a couple similar ones) that
  you find interest you the most\, and we will focus on those in our meetin
 g today.\n\n"❌" doesn't necessarily mean "hard no"\, but instead you will 
 need to spend longer time in developing these into fully grown EPQ topics.
  If there is anything in this category that strongly interests you\, you c
 an still include them in your "top 3"\, and we will see what we can do.
END:VEVENT
