  the two research interests of yours (i.e.\, light rays & catenary)\, and 
 look up relevant literatures\n4. Look up on the mathematical side (e.g. th
 e Euler-Lagrange Equation) of your research\, and make some notes.\n5. Sta
 rt collecting literature and construct a reading log\, making sure to use 
 the CRAAP system.
